"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:55:04.000Z","msg":"兄弟爬山，各有各做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實Jimmy 上星期四晚集會講得好好，我節錄一下<br />\n「當 6.12 早上民陣來到金鐘，市民已經代替民陣兌現了一個承諾，包圍了立法會和政府總部！民陣已經不再是大台，而是逆權運動裡的公民參與者。」<br />\n響呢個無大台嘅逆權運動裡面，只要有心，人人皆可企出黎成為帶領者，無話邊個取代邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家都係呢場運動入面嘅公民參與者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不妨重溫一下<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/videos/783477435432334/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam%2Fvideos%2F783477435432334%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=3a65f3f8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam/videos/783477435432334/</a><br />\n36：35開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23a22d6f68094032d938151efe2e0d39a243aa39","tid":1783891,"uid":138427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:55:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4176652e668a537c3c71d31fb7d4e99f4a983612","tid":1783891,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5fe845bd6696c096895732fd9cb0c79be0ff51d8","tid":1783891,"uid":271807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e94c22a88cbacc9c2510b8a15aefb9e308f64798","tid":1783891,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-15T08:38:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">各位手足，說好了的公開財務報告係一定會做到嘅</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iudHKDF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiudHKDF.jpg&h=9de7c1cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n感謝各位香港人的支持，民間集會團隊先可以一次又一次舉辦各項活動<br />\n尤其感謝大家參與眾籌支持我地，令我地能將集會質素提升<br />\n現在奉上「12.12齊上齊落集會」的財務報告<br />\n供公眾一同監察，參考，如有任何疑問，歡迎留言提出，大家一同討論並檢討日後可以如何改進，令活動更進一步！<br />\n財務報告亦已載於我地於collaction 嘅專頁之中： <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/objective/4980\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam%2Fobjective%2F4980&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=3b377abe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/objective/4980</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n再一次感謝大家！<br />\n光復香港！時代革命！<br />\n<br />\n民間集會團隊<br />\nFacebook <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKCATeam&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=ea3541a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKCATeam</a><br />\nInstagram <a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/hkcat/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fhkcat%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=1ff091df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.instagram.com/hkcat/</a><br />\nTwitter <a href=\"https://twitter.com/HKCATeam\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FHKCATeam&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=6289034b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/HKCATeam</a><br />\n眾籌網站 <a href=\"https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.collaction.hk%2Fs%2FHKCATeam%2F&d=WfKWFoUFzWEJR7ioTMJgWiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=2b7dd958\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.collaction.hk/s/HKCATeam/</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:42:11.000Z","msg":"個人覺得，唔好敢婆媽，你地冒被捕危險，唔通咁都唔信，總之<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山 各自努力 毋忘初心"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T03:56:02.000Z","msg":"當初應承左大家公開嘛<br />\n所以要兌現承諾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c218a898aafd1f7f5ac59425f5fb11e8d943d71c","tid":1783891,"uid":95588,"like":0,"di